However, with the new software
there are some tools we would like to have

00:03:42.160 --> 00:03:43.880
a look at. Just to make sure 

00:03:43.880 --> 00:03:47.379
that we are getting the best out of our images.

00:03:47.379 --> 00:03:49.999
We will have a look at the new and improved HDR tool.

00:03:49.999 --> 00:03:52.839
What I have noticed with the new HDR tool is that

00:03:52.840 --> 00:03:58.379
it is much more natural than the one we had
before. It just gives us that slightly less

00:03:58.379 --> 00:04:00.599
overcooked look. 

